title: Ride from JFK - Driver Khuspreet
text:

He drove very carefully, within speed limits, conversed pleasantly. 
I won,t mind riding with him again.

title: Unhappy customer
text:
We were waiting for the Uber driver and we were at the location by the flyover and the driver was nowhere to be found 
We texted him and told him our location at that time he cancelled our ride and we still had to pay a cancellation fee when it was the driver that cancelled. 
This is poor customer service and I would like my money refunded due to your drivers negligence
